com.cerner.beadledom.jaxrs

Class GenericResponses

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cerner.beadledom.jaxrs.GenericResponses

  • public class GenericResponses
extends Object
    A class that contains most of the static utility methods for GenericResponse corresponding to the utility methods from the Response class.

    This utility class is needed because Java 6 does not allow static methods on interfaces.

    Since:
    1.3
    Author:
    John Leacox
